Class DLList.Elem

  • java.lang.Object
    • DLList.Elem
  • Enclosing class:
    DLList<T>

    private class DLList.Elem
extends java.lang.Object
    Class which implements the structure of a linked list. Has pointers to the next and previous element in the list, and also holds an object which is of the type of object being stored by this list.
    Author:
    David
